title: Making Jake An Honest Man
description:
The love doctor makes a guest appearance to get Jake his long awaited date with Sydney. Plus, bringing back the art of human interaction and networking, how to keep your fitness routine effective AND enjoyable, and Giancarlo’s mom’s knowledge of fitness is tested. Who knows more: Our audience members or her?
